    N1["1. Technical objective: Backend-neutral L2 batch transition primitives shared by fast execution and proof generation."]
    N2["2. Determinism: same input model produces the same output model"]
    N3["3. Input constraints: L2 batch | previous state root | execution parameters"]
    N4["4. Transition rule: explicit rules turn accepted input into checkable output"]
    N5["5. Verifiable output: execution trace | new state root | public proof inputs"]
    N6["6. Minimal trust: trust only data that crossed validation boundaries"]
    N7["7. Layer separation: each layer carries one clear technical responsibility"]
    N8["8. Observable evidence: input digest, output digest, state change, and rejection reason"]
